Lisle C++ library
=================

Multi threading in C++

Description
-----------
A cross-platform C++ library for multi-threading.
Provides thread management features:
- creation
- suspension
- cancellation
- termination
Provides thread synchronization devices:
- mutex, retex (recursive mutex)
- acquirer, releaser
- semaphore
- condition
- event
- shorex (shared or exclusive lock)
- barrier
Supported platforms:
- posix (linux)
- windows
Supported compilers:
- gcc
- visual studio
